author: stux
title: Fantastic Set
review:
This is a fantastic set.

The build quality is so good, the car rolls, the caravan is fantastic, and the mummy, daddy and baby figures are soooo cute.

Our 1 yr old daughter loves this set, it has a nice car, a big caravan, bbq, pot, table, chairs, baby, mummy, daddy, etc.

I almost think we need to go on a camping trip so she can understand what a caravan is!
